Twenty-eight–year-old BBN season 4 winner Mercy Eke has claimed she is a billionaire. In a back and forth conversation with followers, she corrected a fan who insinuated that she was not yet a billionaire. Mercy announced that she had been added to her secondary school whatsapp group and will be happy to reunite with them. She said: ” I have just been added to my secondary school whatsapp group. It’s good to be back, lots of memories. I’m really happy to reunite with the girls. EGSS 2008″   Five renamed major landmarks in Lagos     I’m not married, Mr Macaroni declares     Anthony Joshua always my champion, says DJ Cuppy   A fan identified as Taureen replied to her post: ” They have a famous billionaire in their midst. They will be proud”. A fan Timi Coker then reminded everyone that she was not a billionaire, stating : Replying to the statement, Mercy simply said: “I am.”